<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink148-kilavi">
        varainteytiya talaimakaṉ talaiviyōṭu paḷḷiyiṭattiruntuḻit tōḻi vāḻttiyatu </p>    <p xml:lang="en">
          The praise made by confidante, when the hero, having obtained [a status of] marriage, was in the bedroom with the heroine.  </p>
 </div>     
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink149">
<l>ekkar ñāḻaṟ pūvi ṉaṉṉa</l>
<l>cuṇaṅkuvaḷa riḷamulai maṭantaik</l>
<l>kaṇaṅkuvaḷart takaṟal vallā tīmē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l> Do not have the ability to leave</l>
        <l> - Having made raised torment [within her] - </l>
        <l> The lady with young breasts upon which beauty-spots grow</l>
        <l>Like Ñāḻal flowers in the dunes.</l>
               </lg>
    </div>
